    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058372_26_2278-2369",
      "chapterUid": 26,
      "range": "2278-2369",
      "markText": "在这次科举考试中，欧阳修和他的助手梅尧臣录取了一大批历史上有名的人物。其中有：苏轼、苏辙、曾巩、曾布、吕惠卿、程颢、王回、张载、蒋之奇等。他们在以后发生的许多事件中扮演着不同的角色。",
      "totalCount": 198,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058372&chapterUid=26&rangeStart=2278&rangeEnd=2369",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9c32a50813ab7d4dg01243a?chapterUid=26&rangeStart=2278&rangeEnd=2369"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058372_3_442-494",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "442-494",
      "markText": "男儿少壮不树立，挟此穷老将安归？——王安石",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058372&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=442&rangeEnd=494",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9c32a50813ab7d4dg01243a?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=442&rangeEnd=494"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058372_13_4903-4935",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "4903-4935",
      "markText": "世间之事，要名实相符，批评才可以罪人。如果名实不符，又何必解释！",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058372&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=4903&rangeEnd=4935",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9c32a50813ab7d4dg01243a?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=4903&rangeEnd=4935"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058372_34_1033-1072",
      "chapterUid": 34,
      "range": "1033-1072",
      "markText": "神宗皇帝稍加思索后，便赐此书之名曰“资治通鉴”，这就是《资治通鉴》一书的来历。",
      "totalCount": 144,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058372&chapterUid=34&rangeStart=1033&rangeEnd=1072",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9c32a50813ab7d4dg01243a?chapterUid=34&rangeStart=1033&rangeEnd=1072"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058372_61_2597-2678",
      "chapterUid": 61,
      "range": "2597-2678",
      "markText": "同年九月，在王安石死后五个多月，司马光除了没把河湟地区还给西夏外，把整个新法和王安石执政时所建立的一切全都废除，尽行恢复旧制。他似乎也完成了一种夙愿，寿终正寝了。",
      "totalCount": 140,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058372&chapterUid=61&rangeStart=2597&rangeEnd=2678",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9c32a50813ab7d4dg01243a?chapterUid=61&rangeStart=2597&rangeEnd=2678"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058372_8_5341-5385",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "5341-5385",
      "markText": "在官场中，政绩如何是无关紧要的，黜陟升谪的关键是人际关系，是由与当权者的感情如何决定的。",
      "totalCount": 135,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058372&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5341&rangeEnd=5385",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9c32a50813ab7d4dg01243a?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5341&rangeEnd=5385"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058372_4_3430-3505",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3430-3505",
      "markText": "“是的。爹爹说的对，我一定要好好读书，发奋求学，一定要赶上爷爷，赶上爹爹，不能让王氏家族在我们这一代衰落。”想到这里，小王安石咬了咬牙，绷了绷小嘴唇。",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058372&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3430&rangeEnd=3505",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9c32a50813ab7d4dg01243a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3430&rangeEnd=3505"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058372_5_3460-3508",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3460-3508",
      "markText": "在大街上，经常可以看到男女青年拉着手走路，有的甚至勾肩搭背，在公共场所便随意调笑戏谑，毫无顾忌。",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058372&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3460&rangeEnd=3508",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9c32a50813ab7d4dg01243a?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3460&rangeEnd=3508"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058372_16_5038-5113",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "5038-5113",
      "markText": "如果县衙以官府的名义向需要借款的百姓放贷，把利息率定在百分之二十，即百姓所说的二分利的话，借款的百姓在利息方面就可以减轻一半的负担，无疑是功德无量的事",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058372&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=5038&rangeEnd=5113",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9c32a50813ab7d4dg01243a?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=5038&rangeEnd=5113"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058372_25_3590-3676",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "3590-3676",
      "markText": "王安石发现，司马光学识渊博，尤其精于史学，对古代历史有极深的造诣。二人也曾经在一起喝过酒，酒量都极差。王安石喝不过三杯，过量头就发晕。司马光只是一杯的酒量，多喝半杯脸就红。",
      "totalCount": 120,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058372&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=3590&rangeEnd=3676",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9c32a50813ab7d4dg01243a?chapterUid=25&rangeStart=3590&rangeEnd=3676"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058372_5_3833-3906",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3833-3906",
      "markText": "其大意是说：由于王益到任后政通人和，百兽都受了感动。老虎可能是受了感动，后悔当初的行为，竟有五只老虎自杀而死。县令命当地的百姓割下这五颗虎头来献。",
      "totalCount": 117,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058372&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3833&rangeEnd=3906",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9c32a50813ab7d4dg01243a?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3833&rangeEnd=3906"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058372_7_1360-1387",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "1360-1387",
      "markText": "在古代，迈出一足之距离为跬，两足各迈一次的距离才叫步。",
      "totalCount": 108,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058372&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1360&rangeEnd=1387",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9c32a50813ab7d4dg01243a?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=1360&rangeEnd=1387"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058372_60_2754-2778",
      "chapterUid": 60,
      "range": "2754-2778",
      "markText": "但王安石的想法错了，司马光一上台，就要尽废新法。",
      "totalCount": 104,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058372&chapterUid=60&rangeStart=2754&rangeEnd=2778",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9c32a50813ab7d4dg01243a?chapterUid=60&rangeStart=2754&rangeEnd=2778"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300058372_7_3621-3658",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "3621-3658",
      "markText": "顾客如果再要上几样精细小菜，喝上几盅酒，一结账最起码就要花掉一百两银子了。",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058372&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3621&rangeEnd=3658",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9c32a50813ab7d4dg01243a?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3621&rangeEnd=3658"
    },
    {
