      "chapterUid": 57,
      "range": "6027-6059",
      "markText": "爆竹声中一岁除，春风送暖入屠苏。千门万户曈曈日，总把新桃换旧符。",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300058372&chapterUid=57&rangeStart=6027&rangeEnd=6059",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9c32a50813ab7d4dg01243a?chapterUid=57&rangeStart=6027&rangeEnd=6059"
    },
    {
